        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
          设计模式<span class="exturl post-edit-link" data-url="aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2theWxlaC9rYXlsZWguZ2l0aHViLmlvMi9lZGl0L21hc3Rlci9zb3VyY2UvX3Bvc3RzL+iuvuiuoeaooeW8jy5tZA==" title="Edit this post"><i class="fa fa-pen-nib"></i></span>
